---
import DevLayout from '../../../layouts/DevLayout.astro';
import ExampleFloatingLabels from '../../../components/examples/ExampleFloatingLabels.astro';
---

<DevLayout>
  <ExampleFloatingLabels />
  <section class="component-info-section py-5">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="mb-3">Example Floating Labels Component</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>ExampleFloatingLabels</strong> is a section component that demonstrates modern form inputs with animated floating labels. The labels smoothly animate from placeholder position to floating position when the input is focused or has content.
      </p>
      
      <div class="card mb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="h5 mb-3">Floating Labels Features</h3>
          <ul class="mb-0">
            <li>Follows BEM structure and project section conventions</li>
            <li>Section wrapper: <code>page-sec page-sec--example-floating-labels</code> with <code>container</code></li>
            <li>Smooth label animations with CSS transitions</li>
            <li>Supports multiple input types: text, email, password, tel, date, select, textarea</li>
            <li>Fully accessible with proper focus states and keyboard navigation</li>
            <li>Form validation with visual feedback</li>
            <li>Responsive design that adapts to mobile devices</li>
            <li>Custom styling with brand colors</li>
            <li>All styles in dedicated SCSS partial, imported in <code>main.scss</code></li>
            <li>JavaScript functionality in dedicated module</li>
            <li>Ready for use in design system and real site pages</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card mb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="h5 mb-3">Usage Examples</h3>
          
          <h6 class="mt-3">Basic Floating Label Input</h6>
          <pre style="background:#f8f8f8;padding:1rem;border-radius:6px;overflow:auto"><code>{`<div class="form-floating js__example-floating-label">
  <input type="text" class="form-control" id="floatingName" placeholder="Enter your name">
  <label for="floatingName">Full Name</label>
</div>`}</code></pre>

          <h6 class="mt-3">Floating Label Select</h6>
          <pre style="background:#f8f8f8;padding:1rem;border-radius:6px;overflow:auto"><code>{`<div class="form-floating js__example-floating-label">
  <select class="form-select" id="floatingSelect">
    <option value="" selected disabled>Choose an option</option>
    <option value="option1">Option 1</option>
    <option value="option2">Option 2</option>
  </select>
  <label for="floatingSelect">Select an Option</label>
</div>`}</code></pre>

          <h6 class="mt-3">Floating Label Textarea</h6>
          <pre style="background:#f8f8f8;padding:1rem;border-radius:6px;overflow:auto"><code>{`<div class="form-floating js__example-floating-label">
  <textarea class="form-control" id="floatingTextarea" placeholder="Leave a comment here" style="height: 100px"></textarea>
  <label for="floatingTextarea">Comments</label>
</div>`}</code></pre>

          <h6 class="mt-3">Component Usage</h6>
          <pre style="background:#f8f8f8;padding:1rem;border-radius:6px;overflow:auto"><code>{`---
import ExampleFloatingLabels from '../../../components/examples/ExampleFloatingLabels.astro';
---
<ExampleFloatingLabels />`}</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="h5 mb-3">Technical Details</h3>
          <ul class="mb-0">
            <li><strong>CSS Classes:</strong> Uses <code>js__example-floating-label</code> for JavaScript targeting</li>
            <li><strong>Animations:</strong> 0.1s transitions for smooth label movement</li>
            <li><strong>Accessibility:</strong> Proper focus states, keyboard navigation, and ARIA labels</li>
            <li><strong>Form Validation:</strong> Client-side validation with visual feedback</li>
            <li><strong>JavaScript:</strong> Module-based initialization with event handling</li>
            <li><strong>Responsive:</strong> Adapts font sizes and spacing for mobile devices</li>
            <li><strong>Brand Colors:</strong> Uses brand blue (#0099f7) for focus states</li>
            <li><strong>Cross-browser:</strong> Works with all modern browsers</li>
            <li><strong>Form Handling:</strong> Includes submit and reset functionality</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</DevLayout> 